| Configuration | Mean ± 95% CI | Min–Max | n |
| ------------- | ------------ | ------- | - |
| Test Model [low] | 150 ± 0 tok/s (95% CI, n=3) | 150.0–150.0 | 3 |
| Test Model [high] | 150 ± 0 tok/s (95% CI, n=3) | 150.0–150.0 | 3 |

Highest measured of the 2 measured configuration(s): **Test Model [low]** at 150 ± 0 tok/s (95% CI, n=3). Opposite end of this measurement: Test Model [high] at 150 ± 0 tok/s (95% CI, n=3).

